Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.84,0:02:28.00,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1}少し迷って　I leave it I leave it
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.00,0:02:29.73,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1}軽そうに見えた
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.73,0:02:31.39,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1}only one heart
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.39,0:02:34.44,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1}無価値じゃない　Don’t regret it regret it
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.44,0:02:36.81,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1}どんな未来だとしても
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.81,0:02:42.77,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1}思い出すべき過去とか
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.23,0:02:49.15,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1}存在しないこと知っても構わない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.34,0:02:50.37,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1}Don’t let go
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.37,0:02:53.97,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1}Wait Wait, what do you want from me
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.97,0:02:56.79,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1}すれ違っても
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.95,0:03:00.56,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1}Ray Ray, bringing me back to life
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.56,0:03:03.26,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1}絆ほど強さ纏って
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.26,0:03:06.71,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1}Wait Wait, what do you want from me
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.01,0:03:09.79,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1}この声を聞いたか
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.79,0:03:13.39,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1}Ray Ray, bringing me back to life
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.39,0:03:14.57,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1}誇れるよう
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.57,0:03:16.32,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1}Drifting like a flawless ray
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.60,0:02:02.00,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1}一次成形的世界線
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.00,0:02:04.37,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1}已無法再倒帶
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.95,0:02:08.37,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1}被賦予的人生腳本
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.37,0:02:10.75,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1}讓其大放異彩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.84,0:02:28.00,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1}感到些許迷茫  I leave it I leave it
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.00,0:02:29.73,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1}儘管看似玩世不恭
Comment: 0,0:02:29.73,0:02:31.39,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1}only one heart
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.39,0:02:34.44,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1}那並非徒勞  Don’t regret it regret it
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.44,0:02:36.81,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1}無論未來如何
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.81,0:02:42.77,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1}那本該喚醒的回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.23,0:02:49.15,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1}就算是飄渺的存在又何妨
Comment: 0,0:02:49.34,0:02:50.37,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1}Don’t let go
